REPLACE INTO `creature_ai_texts` (`entry`,`content_default`,`sound`,`type`,`language`,`comment`,`emote`) VALUES
('-139','We\'re in the home stretch now.','0','0','0','21218','1'),
('-1668','Victory will be ours!','0','1','0','17918','0'),
('-1669','Carry on! Victory at all costs!','0','1','0','17918','0'),
('-1670','Continue the fight! Do not falter!','0','1','0','17918','0'),
('-1671','There is no time to waste!','0','0','0','17918','0'),
('-1672','We must hurry!','0','0','0','17918','0'),
('-1673','We must use this time wisely!','0','0','0','17918','0'),
('-1674','Chubis Chubisimo!  Get those things fixed... we haven\'t got all day!','0','0','0','19645','5'),
('-1675','How much am I paying you?  You call that working?','0','0','0','19645','5'),
('-1676','When I was your age I could have had all of those shredders fixed before breakfast and still had time for all of my other chores.  In the Winterspring snow, no less.  And it\'s uphill both ways there!','0','0','0','19645','5'),
('-1677','Chubis, after you\'re done there, make sure that you put another coat of wax on the Wheeler mobile.  I want to take mama out for a spin tonight.','0','0','0','19645','5'),
('-1678','I just knew that I shouldn\'t have fired Beebo!','0','0','0','19645','5'),
('-1679','Okay, if you can manage to get even one of those fixed, I\'ll let you take a ten minute break.  How\'s that sound?  Pretty good, huh?','0','0','0','19645','5'),
('-1680','A pleasure... to serve the master.','0','0','0','17899','0'),
('-1681','You will... ultimately fail.','0','0','0','17899','0'),
('-1682','My life... to the master.','0','0','0','17899','0'),
('-1683','Me no can take it no more!','0','0','0','17874/17875','1'),
('-1684','Me lose appetite. Corki is poop.','0','0','0','17874/17875','1'),
('-1685','You shut up!','0','0','0','17874/17875','1'),
('-1686','Me don\'t even want to eat him no more.','0','0','0','17874/17875','1'),
('-1687','Hey fatso, how do you go to the bathroom with all that fat!?','0','0','0','18369','0'),
('-1688','Eat me already! I can\'t take being locked up in this cage around you stinky, fat slobs.','0','0','0','18369','0'),
('-1689','I want my daddy!','0','0','0','18369','0'),
('-1690','You fatheads are in trouble if I ever get out of here!','0','0','0','18369','0'),
('-1691','Hey fathead, how about some food!?','0','0','0','18369','0'),
('-1692','Where piggy go?!','0','1','0','20216','53'),
('-1693','You be Grulloc\'s friend!','0','1','0','20216','0'),
('-1694','Mmm, other white meat!','0','1','0','20216','0'),
('-1695','Grulloc having lots of fun!','0','1','0','20216','0'),
('-1696','Me hungry!','0','1','0','20216','0'),
('-1697','Me keep piggy as pet!','0','1','0','20216','0'),
('-1698','Porkchops!','0','1','0','20216','0'),
('-1699','Piggy stop!','0','1','0','20216','0'),
('-1700','Me like soft bacon!','0','1','0','20216','0'),
('-1701','Put a little elbow grease into it!  And maybe some regular grease, while you\'re at it.  Those mag\'har sure like the clefthoof fat.','0','0','0','24393','22'),
('-1702','Are those ingredients chopped up and cooked?  What\'s the hold up?!','0','0','0','24393','22'),
('-1703','We have a dozen more dishes to finish today!  Get a move on!','0','0','0','24393','22'),
('-1704','Can\'t make water boil any faster, genius!','0','0','0','24416','15'),
('-1705','Yeah, yeah!  Shut yer trap and let me finish this stew!','0','0','0','24416','15'),
('-1706','It\'ll be done when it\'s done, darn it!','0','0','0','24416','15'),
('-1707','Hey fatso, is there any reason why you insist on living in a dung filled hole in the wall?','0','0','0','20812','0'),
('-1708','Can I get some food, please??? This is outrageous!','0','0','0','20812','0'),
('-1709','I don\'t know what smells worse: Your feet or a dung-filled cheese and fish fillet.','0','0','0','20812','0'),
('-1710','Congratulations. It smells worse in here than in the ruins.','0','0','0','20812','0'),
('-1711','%s begins to whistle a tune, but then stops abruptly and moans.','0','2','0','18218','0'),
('-1712','%s groans in pain.','0','2','0','18218','0'),
('-1713','%s winces when he touches the tender area around his scratch.','0','2','0','18218','0'),
('-1714','%s moans from the pain of his thorn scratch.','0','2','0','18218','0'),
('-1715','Shifting, %s moans from the pain of his thorn scratch.','0','2','0','18218','0'),
('-1716','%s looks at his friends and then grunts painfully.','0','2','0','18218','0'),
('-1717','%s wakes himself up snoring.','0','2','0','18218','0'),
('-1718','Well done, soldiers! We weren\'t about to let the filthy animals of the Horde show us up!','0','0','7','19316','22'),
('-1719','We\'re gonna melt this hunk of junk down and make weapons with the ingots! Let\'s see how the Legion likes a taste of fel reaver served up Alliance style!','0','0','7','19316','22'),
('-1720','Tear it down, soldiers! We\'re shippin\' this thing back to Stormwind!','0','0','7','19316','22'),
('-1721','Let them throw another one of these overgrown tin cans at us! We\'ll show them what the Alliance is made of!','0','0','7','19316','22'),
('-1722','Your blood will coat the walls of Kil\'sorrow!','0','0','0','18391','0'),
('-1723','Lady Vashj expects our work to be done soon.','0','0','0','21218','1'),
('-1724','Steady the pumps.','0','0','0','21218','1'),
('-1725','Maintain focus.','0','0','0','21218','1'),
('-1726','You should be honored to be doing Lady Vashj\'s bidding.','0','0','0','21218','1'),
('-1727','Our work is not yet complete.','0','0','0','21218','1'),
('-1728','Keep those pumps working.','0','0','0','21218','1'),
('-1729','We must work faster.','0','0','0','21218','1'),
('-277','Antelarion says I fell off a big bird, as I fell he caught me... He is so pretty!','0','0','0','22465','0'),  
('-278','Antelarion, is it safe to play in the forest yet?','0','0','0','22465','0'),  
('-279','I\'m only 4 years old.','0','0','0','22465','0'),  
('-280','I think I came from Eng-land, do you know where that is?','0','0','0','22465','0'),
('-1730','Enough! I have had enough of you filthy warm bloods!','0','1','0','21218','0'),
('-334','Do you think that demons will play fair? These beasts are more savage than the orcs, more cunning than the undead. Do not attempt to engage Legion by normal standards of war.','0','0','0','19308','0'),
('-335','How many more soldiers need to die before we start paying attention out there?','0','0','0','19308','0'),
('-336','This war - and don\'t mistake this for anything but war - is not going to win itself. If we do not fight, scratch, claw, and kick for every speck of land on this shattered world, all will be lost.','0','0','0','19308','0'),
('-1731','I regret to inform you all that we sent home another ten soldiers today - in body bags.','0','0','0','19308','1');
