('-1776','Yarrrr, mon!','0','0','0','24525','0'),
('-1777','Watch nah, ye bogfiddler!  I an\' I gunna show ye \'ow a jig meant fe be jigged to!','0','0','0','24525','0'),
('-1778','Yah, me bredren!  Galang now and pass us a grog, just dead men yahso.','0','0','0','24525','0'),
('-1780','Dis a rankin\' set, mon, no scurvy dog gonna kass-kass me buckos an\' walk aweh!','0','0','0','24525','0'),
('-1781','...so he says \"Of course I\'m not seeing double!  I\'ve only got one eye!\"','0','0','0','24642','0'),
('-1782','...that scurvy dog had two peg legs, a hook for a left hand, two glass eyes and a wooden nose!','0','0','0','24642','0'),
('-1783','Grab a seat and \'ave a drink, mate!  Grab me one while yer at it!','0','0','0','24642','0'),
('-1784','I \'eard Terry fenced one of \'em pictures for a thousand gold.  Maybe I can get in some of that artwork dealin\' too!','0','0','0','24642','0'),
('-1785','Kiss the gunner\'s daughter?  Why I haven\'t ever met the lass...','0','0','0','24642','0'),
('-1786','Nothin\' finer than enjoying a fine beverage and the company of some fine buckos... hic!','0','0','0','24642','0'),
('-1787','Whatcha lookin\' at, ye bilge rat?  Har, har.... just kiddin\' with ye, mate!','0','0','0','24642','0'),
('-1788','Yarrrrrrr!  Ye\'ll never get me spyglass, bilgesucker!','0','1','0','24742','0'),
('-1789','Looks like me boys need a hand!','0','0','0','24790','0');
